overview: TRANSEXUAL GIRLFRIEND EXPERIENCE #9 continues with very real and current stories focusing on the joys of having a tran girlfriend. Four different scenarios are explored in the latest installment of the groundbreaking trans cinema line. Meet Daisy who while visiting LA gets caught up in a whirlwind romance. Jenna who is feeling the pressure from her mother to marry the man she has been living with. But does he want to marry her? Angelina who like any girl has gone out and found the house she wants her man to build her nest in. Ella, the youngster who has found love with her oversexed older boyfriend who loves dressing her in provocative clothes.
title: Transsexual Girlfriend Experience 9
